## Steps
The first thing we need to do to start developing for Android is to install CodeWorks for Android 1R6u1, which will ensure that we have all the required programs and code needed to deploy to Android devices. In the following section, we will cover how to get CodeWorks for Android 1R6u1 installed on a development PC.


